{"article_id":"sFqW7m5bRUlSUE7D","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"More than 100 Americans have tried to join militants in Syria ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"U.S. officials say","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Pentagon official :","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"McCain `` a stark reminder of the inside threat ( from ) foreign fighters ''","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"U.S. official :","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Threat of jihadis","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"returning to U.S. `` front and center of our agenda ''","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"McCain converted to Islam years ago ;","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"family saw Facebook posts sympathetic to ISIS","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"An American man died last weekend in Syria","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"while fighting for ISIS , the latest evidence of the reach of a terror group","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that 's become increasingly powerful","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and feared in the eyes of Americans .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Douglas McAuthur McCain , 33 , died in a battle between rival extremist groups in the suburbs of Aleppo , Syria 's once-bustling commercial capital and largest city ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"according to the Syrian Observatory for Human Rights , a British-based group","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that monitors the conflict .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The man 's uncle , Ken McCain , said","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"that his nephew had gone to fight as a jihadi","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and that the U.S. State Department told the family Monday about the death .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"Who are the Americans","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"fighting for ISIS ?","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"MUST WATCH Who are the Americans fighting for ISIS ?","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"02:50","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"Other Americans already within ISIS ranks","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"Other Americans already within ISIS ranks","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"02:14","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"JUST WATCHED Westerners with ISIS a 'growing threat '","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"MUST WATCH Westerners with ISIS a 'growing threat ' 03:54","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Like U.S. officials , the group characterized McCain as an ISIS fighter","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"and said","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"he was killed","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"battling al-Nusra Front , an al Qaeda-linked organization","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"that the U.S. government has blacklisted as a foreign terror organization .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"McCain was not the first American","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"to fight alongside militants in Syria .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Attorney General Eric Holder estimated this summer","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that there are 7,000 foreign fighters in the war-ravaged Middle Eastern nation .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"More than 100 Americans are among those","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"who have tried to join various militant groups in Syria ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"U.S. officials say .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"While some are aligned with ISIS ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"the fighters shift allegiance","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"and it 's difficult to pin down a specific number ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"officials say .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Nor was McCain the first of these American militants","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to die in Syria .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Islamists touted the role of a 22-year-old man","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"-- identified by State Department spokeswoman Jen Psaki as Moner Mohammad Abu-Salha ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"who grew up","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"and went to school in Florida --","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"in a northern Syria suicide bombing","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"conducted in coordination with al-Nusra Front .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Yet McCain 's death takes on added significance , perhaps urgency ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"given that he 's believed to be the first American","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"killed while fighting with ISIS .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Until now , Washington largely has limited its involvement in Syria to diplomatic efforts and supporting `` moderate opposition , ''","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"as described by Joint Chiefs of Staff Chairman Martin Dempsey and others ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that is fighting to unseat Syrian President Bashar al-Assad .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"That 's the same goal as ISIS ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"which aims to rule a caliphate ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"known as the Islamic State ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"spanning Iraq and Syria .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Even so , the United States initiated airstrikes against ISIS in Iraq this month","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and signaled","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that it might next go after the group inside Syria .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"And it has begun gathering intelligence on ISIS in Syria , potentially ahead of more airstrikes there .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"ISIS has threatened to kill more Americans","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"if the U.S. continues to go after it .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"But the fact","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"McCain was among its ranks","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"adds another fear :","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"That the group includes other Americans","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"who ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"rather than dying on the battlefield ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"might inflict harm stateside .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` There 's real concern","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"that they could take what they 've learned ...","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"come back home","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"and conduct terror attacks , ''","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"Pentagon spokesman Rear Adm. John Kirby told CNN .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"`` So I think","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"( McCain )","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"is a stark reminder of the inside threat","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"that foreign fighters","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"( in ISIS )","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"can pose . ''","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"Little was immediately known publicly about McCain 's life , beyond how it ended .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"He attended San Diego City College ,","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"though its spokesman Jack Beresford would not say","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"when McCain attended , for how long or for what purpose .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Several years ago ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"according to his uncle ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"McCain converted from Christianity to Islam","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"-- the first step on his journey to Syria .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"The family was n't alarmed by his conversion ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"but his Facebook posts sympathetic to ISIS got their attention .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"When they last heard from him several months ago ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"McCain said","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"he was traveling to Turkey ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"according to his uncle .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Kean :","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"`` Appalled '' at lack of ISIS knowledge","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"Kean :","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"`` Appalled '' at lack of ISIS knowledge","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"03:36","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Is there support for ISIS in London ?","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"Is there support for ISIS in London ?","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"02:38","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Dealing with ISIS and Assad in Syria","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"Dealing with ISIS and Assad in Syria","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"05:25","depth":16},{"id":127,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"CNN speaks to British jihadi fighter","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"CNN speaks to British jihadi fighter","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"03:05","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"The fact","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"that McCain became a jihadi","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"left his family `` devastated ''","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and `` just as surprised as the country , ''","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"said Ken McCain ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"who lives in Minnesota .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"He described the nephew","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"he knew","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"as `` a good person ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"loved his family ,","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"loved his mother ,","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"loved his faith ''","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"-- the latter being a reference to the Christianity","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"he practiced before his conversion .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"U.S. counterterrorism investigators had been looking into McCain 's activities for some time before his death ,","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"one U.S. official said .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"He was on a list of Americans","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"who are believed to have joined militant groups","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"and who would be stopped","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"and subjected to additional scrutiny","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"if he traveled ,","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"according to the official .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"Retired U.S. Army Brig . Gen. Mark Kimmitt ,","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"who had top roles in the State and Defense Departments in President George W. Bush 's administration ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"he expects more stories like McCain 's .","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"`` The ability","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"to travel into these countries","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"demonstrates how porous the borders are , ''","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"Kimmitt said .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"we need to understand","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"that there 's going to be more of this rather than less of this . ''","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"Syria 's civil war has been brewing for three years .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"In the absence of a unified rebel front , many groups","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"-- some moderate , some more secular , some extremist --","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"have tried to fill the void .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"Much of the time , they 've battled al-Assad 's forces ,","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"though there has also been infighting among them .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"Among these rebel groups , one has emerged recently in the public 's consciousness :","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"ISIS .","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"That 's as much due to its brazenness and viciousness as to its success .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"The general command for al Qaeda","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"-- itself responsible for the September 11 , 2001 , terrorist attacks --","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"went so far as to disown ISIS","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"and blame it for `` the enormity of the disaster","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"that afflicted the Jihad in Syria . ''","depth":15},{"id":180,"text":"It has taken more and more territory in Iraq and Syria ,","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"sometimes overrunning government forces","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"while terrorizing civilians .","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"ISIS 's stature grew even more internationally with the recent beheading of American journalist James Foley ,","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"a killing","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"it videotaped","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"and then put online .","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"`` They are beyond just a terrorist group , ''","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"Defense Secretary Chuck Hagel said last week .","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"`` They marry ideology , a sophistication of strategic and tactical military prowess .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"`` This is beyond anything","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"we have seen ,","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"and we must prepare for everything . ''","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"These preparations include tracking Westerners like McCain .","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"In addition to whatever they might do against allies and civilians in the Middle East ,","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"U.S. officials worry","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"that they could bring their groups ' brand of terror back home .","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"Assistant Attorney General John Carlin said last month","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"that getting intelligence on such Americans","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"who fight in Syria","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"and making sure","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"they do n't bring that right back home is `` a top priority . '' `` We have increased our capacity ,","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"we have increased our tracking ,","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"we have increased our coordination , ''","depth":15},{"id":204,"text":"Psaki said .","depth":12},{